    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a museum-quality 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black Metallic. This example is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. This specimen is mechanically superlative; the rod bearing service has been proactively completed, and the rear subframe has been structurally reinforced to exceed factory specifications. The suspension geometry remains true, utilizing OEM Sachs dampers for a compliant yet communicative chassis response. The exterior maintains factory-original paint depth with zero evidence of oxidation or rock chips. The interior is upholstered in pristine Nappa leather with no bolster wear, and the instrument cluster is free of pixel degradation. An unmolested, turn-key masterpiece for the purist collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
